      "section": [
        "Relics"
      ],
      "text": "\"Relics\" is a comic book that takes place in Book One: Water, originally released by Nickelodeon Magazine. It was later recycled for Free Comic Book Day 2011, and was finally re-released by Dark Horse Comics in Avatar: The Last Airbender \u2014 The Lost Adventures."
